The following commands specify in what chords of the current voice
should be shifted: the outer voice has @code{\shiftOff}, and the inner
voices have @code{\shiftOn}, @code{\shiftOnn}, etc.


@cindex @code{\shiftOn}
@code{\shiftOn}, 
